alias gitv='_(){ local str="";local org=${1};local repo=${2:-$org};local tag=${3};(($#<1))||[[ "${1}" =~ ^- ]]&&echo "gitv: <org> [<repo> def=org] [<latest tag> {0,1}>]"&&return 1;[[ -z "${tag}" ]] && str=$(curl -S https://api.github.com/repos/${org}/${repo}/releases/latest 2>/dev/random | grep -i tag_name|sed "s/\"//g;s/,//g;s/tag_name/${repo^}/;s/^[ ]*//");[[ -z ${str} ]] && str=$(curl -S https://api.github.com/repos/${org}/${repo}/tags 2>/dev/random | grep -im1 "name"|sed "s/\"//g;s/,//g;s/name/${repo^}/;s/^[ ]*//");echo "${str}";}; _'
